    fitted item icons, and roll-range badges. Used by:
      * Combat tab via armour-display-panel.hbs (wrapped in panel.hbs)
      * Overview tab via tab-overview.hbs (wrapped in dashboard-zone)

    Required context:
        armourDisplay — { head | rightArm | leftArm | body | rightLeg | leftLeg }
                        each with `.total`, `.items[]`, `.tooltipData`.

    Optional context:
        compact — when true, drop the extra fitted-items strip and roll-range
                  badge to fit dashboard-zone footprints (Overview tab).
--}}
